com.stripe.stripeterminal.model.external

Class PaymentMethod

  • com.stripe.stripeterminal.model.external.PaymentMethod

  • public class PaymentMethod

    PaymentMethod objects represent your customer's payment instruments. They can be used with class PaymentIntents to collect payments, or saved to Customer objects to store instrument details for future payments.

    For more information, see the official Stripe docs: Payment methods Attach payment method

    Use of this SDK is subject to the Stripe Terminal Terms: https://stripe.com/terminal/legal

    See Also:
    class PaymentIntent, Payment methods, Attach payment method
